title: Fantastic Four Unlimited 1-12 (1993)
description:
This is my first attempt at uploading a torrent, so I figured I'd start with something that I had to dig to find.

All credit goes to the original uploader and scanners. These were pulled from the Dimlan Chronology Disks and took a lot of searching before I found them.

Anyway, here we have "The Fantastic Four Unlimited" comics which ran from 1993 to 1995 with quarterly releases.

If this torrent has some errors please leave a comment, like I said, this is my first attempt and I'm bound to make mistakes!

Also, since I have the floor here I just wanted to say thank you to a few Pirate Bay users:
